data.description: This affordable, well-maintained Jefferson/Franklin Model townhome offers a perfect blend of comfort and convenience. Say goodbye to monthly rent payments and hello to homeownership! Imagine the satisfaction of investing in your future, where every dollar you spend goes towards owning your own piece of paradise. The 1st Floor features a living room with 9' Ceilings and a powder room. The kitchen has 42" Maple Kitchen Cabinets with self-cleaning range dishwasher, breakfast bar with plenty of cabinet space and dining area. Second floor features three (3) bedrooms and a full hall bath. With a tasteful combination of Pergo floors and carpeting throughout the home. The basement is unfinished with laundry area and is perfect for storage which can be easily converted to a fully finished living area. Low HOA fees cover trash, snow, and landscaping. One-time capital contribution fee  from Buyer. The Penn Crossing community is FHA approved! Gas heat, Central air, storage shed, Concrete Foundation with Superior Walls and Insulation, 25 Yr. Dimensional Shingles, Security System and one (1) assigned parking space and off-street parking. Conveniently located near Route 30 so residents can enjoy easy access to everything the area has to offer along with nearby parks and schools, creating a welcoming environment for all ages. Perfectly suited for first-time buyers and downsizing, this residence offers a warm and inviting atmosphere where you can begin building lasting new memories. Schedule a showing today and make this your new home sweet home!
